# Supported Platforms

* CentOS 7

# Parameters

* conf:
    cluster(dict or None): If None, do not join cluster
      name(string, 'elasticsearch'): Name of the cluster
      nodes(list):
        name(string): name of the cluster node
        min_masters(int): Minimum amount of potential masters to reach quorum.
                          If omitted, a sensible default will be used.
    nodename(string, '${HOSTNAME}'): name of the node in the cluster
    master(bool, True): Act as master node
    data(bool, True): Act as data node
    local(bool, False): Allow query only from localhost

* iptables:
    local(bool, False): Allow query only from localhost
